<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 02:23:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>七名以色列人回忆起他们在哈马斯被囚禁期间的磨难：“每天都有人在身体和灵魂上杀死一些东西”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/seven-israelis-recall-their-ordeal-in-hamas-captivity-every-day-kills-something-inside/0000018c-f9d9-dd94-a9cc-fbfd31340000</link><description>战争已经过去近 100 天了，而且还被关押在加沙地带。七名人质返回，但将父母、孩子、兄弟姐妹和朋友留在加沙，他们描述了他们所经历的一切，并敦促采取一切措施立即将剩余的俘虏带回家</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 00:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/seven-israelis-recall-their-ordeal-in-hamas-captivity-every-day-kills-something-inside/0000018c-f9d9-dd94-a9cc-fbfd31340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方禁止针对加沙战争的抗议活动，理由是无法保护公众、防止暴力，</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-bars-protests-against-gaza-war-says-police-cant-protect-public-prevent-violence/0000018c-fa19-d1b3-a79e-fedbd1e40000</link><description>人权组织猛烈抨击阻止犹太和阿拉伯团体在海法示威的决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 22:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-bars-protests-against-gaza-war-says-police-cant-protect-public-prevent-violence/0000018c-fa19-d1b3-a79e-fedbd1e40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长可能无法避免对内塔尼亚胡是否适合任职的裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-may-not-be-able-to-avoid-ruling-on-netanyahus-fitness-for-office/0000018c-fa0a-dd94-a9cc-faee69fb0000</link><description>几个月后，如果内塔尼亚胡政府仍然完好无损，总理将不得不每天花几个小时在审判中作证，同时还要管理国家 ■ 最高法院可能已经停止了司法改革，但对裁决的仔细审查也令人担忧</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 21:08:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-may-not-be-able-to-avoid-ruling-on-netanyahus-fitness-for-office/0000018c-fa0a-dd94-a9cc-faee69fb0000</guid></item><item><title>南非是否已经破坏了以色列对国际法院种族灭绝指控的防御？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-11/ty-article/.highlight/has-south-africa-already-wrecked-israels-defense-against-icj-charges-of-genocide/0000018c-f9cc-d1b3-a79e-ffded2f10000</link><description>以色列的自卫并未受到审判，也不能成为违反《种族灭绝公约》任何部分的理由。简而言之，以色列的国防几乎没有提供任何防御</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 20:39:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-11/ty-article/.highlight/has-south-africa-already-wrecked-israels-defense-against-icj-charges-of-genocide/0000018c-f9cc-d1b3-a79e-ffded2f10000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔即将与哈马斯敲定协议，向加沙的以色列人质运送药品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/qatar-close-to-finalizing-deal-with-hamas-to-transfer-medicine-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018c-f9e9-dd94-a9cc-fbed7be90000</link><description>据报道，该协议包括以色列允许更多药品进入加沙，以换取向以色列人质提供处方药</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 19:34:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/qatar-close-to-finalizing-deal-with-hamas-to-transfer-medicine-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018c-f9e9-dd94-a9cc-fbed7be90000</guid></item><item><title>“最大的讽刺在于酷儿本身”：10 月 7 日之后，LGBTQ 以色列人受到国际社会的回避</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/lgbtq-israelis-describe-being-shunned-by-global-community-after-october-7/0000018c-f92a-dd94-a9cc-fbee4d680000</link><description>以色列策展人亚登·斯特恩 (Yarden Stern) 表示，“一年来，近一百万人抗议以色列极右政府”。 “全球酷儿社区并没有向我们伸出援手，而是完全无视我们。”就像我们是我们的政府的一员，而不是那些长期以来一直试图创造变革的人”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 19:29:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/lgbtq-israelis-describe-being-shunned-by-global-community-after-october-7/0000018c-f92a-dd94-a9cc-fbee4d680000</guid></item><item><title>随着国际航空公司恢复飞往以色列的航班，价格下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/prices-drop-as-international-airlines-resume-flights-to-israel/0000018c-f95d-dd94-a9cc-fbfd0b7c0000</link><description>飞往以色列的航班竞争加剧，导致机票价格较12月份全面大幅下跌，而飞往尚未竞争的目的地的票价则保持不变</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:40:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/prices-drop-as-international-airlines-resume-flights-to-israel/0000018c-f95d-dd94-a9cc-fbfd0b7c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列冰球联合会向体育仲裁法院提出上诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-ice-hockey-federation-appeals-to-court-of-arbitration-for-sport/0000018c-f949-dd94-a9cc-fbed46f70000</link><description>在 U20 男子世界锦标赛举行前 12 天，国际冰球联合会宣布禁止以色列参加比赛，“出于对所有参赛者安全的担忧” ■ 以色列称这一决定是“反犹太主义”，并向 CAS 提出上诉</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:37:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-ice-hockey-federation-appeals-to-court-of-arbitration-for-sport/0000018c-f949-dd94-a9cc-fbed46f70000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡支持本格维尔，表示以色列监狱长不会延长任期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/backing-ben-gvir-netanyahu-says-israels-prison-chief-wont-have-term-extended/0000018c-f95d-d517-af9d-fd7f92de0000</link><description>尽管战时内阁同意不改变像她这样的高级职位，但凯蒂·佩里作为最高监狱长的任期预计将于一月下旬结束</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:43:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/backing-ben-gvir-netanyahu-says-israels-prison-chief-wont-have-term-extended/0000018c-f95d-d517-af9d-fd7f92de0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部阿拉伯城市汽车爆炸 男子丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/man-killed-in-car-explosion-in-arab-city-in-central-israel/0000018c-f94d-dd94-a9cc-fbed31050000</link><description>蒂拉发生大规模爆炸，导致一名 30 多岁男子丧生，这是本周这座阿拉伯城市发生的第二起凶杀案</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/man-killed-in-car-explosion-in-arab-city-in-central-israel/0000018c-f94d-dd94-a9cc-fbed31050000</guid></item><item><title>艾曼·奥德仍然相信两国解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ayman-odeh-still-believes-in-the-two-state-solution/0000018c-f3f1-da04-a7df-f3f54f5a0000</link><description>艾曼·奥德 (Ayman Odeh) 16 岁时，被辛​​贝特 (Shin Bet) 安全部门叫去进行一系列关于他的政治活动的谈话。 40 多岁时，他是以色列犹太人最喜欢的阿拉伯政治家。现在他退出政党政治，但这并不是因为他放弃了更美好未来的梦想</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:25:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ayman-odeh-still-believes-in-the-two-state-solution/0000018c-f3f1-da04-a7df-f3f54f5a0000</guid></item><item><title>与真主党的战争是不可避免的。但以色列应该发起这一行动吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-war-with-hezbollah-is-inevitable-but-should-israel-initiate-it/0000018c-f7d5-d432-a7ae-fffdf0e50000</link><description>以色列现在应对真主党及其挑衅有重要的战略理由。但黎巴嫩战争可能会将美国自由派选民中不断高涨的反以色列情绪转变为一场完美风暴。这将是一场以色列从未经历过的冲突</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:45:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-war-with-hezbollah-is-inevitable-but-should-israel-initiate-it/0000018c-f7d5-d432-a7ae-fffdf0e50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子被控刺伤妻子、打伤儿子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-charged-with-stabbing-and-killing-wife-wounding-son/0000018c-f902-df8a-adbf-fb7eb4260000</link><description>起诉书指控 Asher Bohbot 对其 15 岁的儿子犯有严重谋杀罪和严重殴打罪，当时儿子在事件中试图阻止他。一位家人的熟人表示，布布特以前殴打过他的妻子，她曾考虑与他离婚</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:22:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-charged-with-stabbing-and-killing-wife-wounding-son/0000018c-f902-df8a-adbf-fb7eb4260000</guid></item><item><title>从被毁坏的家中撤离后，来自加沙边境的以色列孩子在特拉维夫重新开始学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/evacuated-from-a-devastated-home-israeli-kids-from-gaza-border-restart-school-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f8e3-dd94-a9cc-faef01000000</link><description>大约三周前，大约 400 名雷伊姆居民从最南端城市埃拉特的酒店房间收拾行李，他们在 10 月 7 日袭击事件后从家中撤离后一直住在那里，开始了生活的新篇章。这次是在特拉维夫的赫茨尔街</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/evacuated-from-a-devastated-home-israeli-kids-from-gaza-border-restart-school-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f8e3-dd94-a9cc-faef01000000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院驳回内塔尼亚胡违反利益冲突协议的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-rejects-petition-saying-netanyahu-broke-conflict-of-interest-deal/0000018c-f89c-d30b-a59d-f8de8e6f0000</link><description>“据我们所知，自10月7日以来，以色列一直处于战争状态，这对我们面前的案件产生了重大影响。在这些影响中，作为请愿者主张核心的立法程序目前并未得到推进，”高等法院法官说</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:56:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-rejects-petition-saying-netanyahu-broke-conflict-of-interest-deal/0000018c-f89c-d30b-a59d-f8de8e6f0000</guid></item><item><title>“南非是哈马斯的合法机构”：以色列谴责国际法院加沙种族灭绝听证会“扭曲”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-is-hamas-legal-arm-israel-blasts-distorted-icj-gaza-genocide-hearing/0000018c-f898-d30b-a59d-f8dec5b30000</link><description>以色列外交部发言人称南非律师为“哈马斯”代表，周五第二天听证会前已做出初步回应</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:35:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-is-hamas-legal-arm-israel-blasts-distorted-icj-gaza-genocide-hearing/0000018c-f898-d30b-a59d-f8dec5b30000</guid></item><item><title>汗尤尼斯的“720度”战斗，可能决定以色列与哈马斯战争的结果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fighting-in-720-degrees-in-khan-yunis-where-what-happens-may-decide-outcome-of-war/0000018c-f881-dd94-a9cc-faed2e6f0000</link><description>双桅船。驻扎在加沙地带南部的以色列陆军第 98 师指挥官丹·戈德福斯 (Dan Goldfus) 将军每天都在解决像魔方一样的问题，因为他负责监督一支在地面、空中和哈马斯地道中行动的臃肿部队</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fighting-in-720-degrees-in-khan-yunis-where-what-happens-may-decide-outcome-of-war/0000018c-f881-dd94-a9cc-faed2e6f0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列政府意图消灭加沙的巴勒斯坦人”：南非向国际法院提出种族灭绝案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/israeli-govt-is-intent-on-destroying-palestinians-south-africa-presents-genocide-case/0000018c-f8bc-d517-af9d-fcbe87ae0000</link><description>南非法律团队在海牙进行了开庭陈词，指责以色列实施种族灭绝行为、言论和煽动。他们引用了内塔尼亚胡总理、赫尔佐格总统和几位部长的声明作为证据。以色列将于周五针对这些指控为自己辩护</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 13:49:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/israeli-govt-is-intent-on-destroying-palestinians-south-africa-presents-genocide-case/0000018c-f8bc-d517-af9d-fcbe87ae0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔否认哈马斯领导人流亡条款，以色列回应新的人质释放提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/qatar-denies-hamas-leaders-clause-as-israel-responds-to-new-hostage-release-proposal/0000018c-f87b-d517-af9d-fc7f5e340000</link><description>政治消息人士强调，以色列的一贯立场不是同意哈马斯停止战争的要求，也不是以完全停止在加沙地带的军事活动为前提达成释放人质协议</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 13:21:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/qatar-denies-hamas-leaders-clause-as-israel-responds-to-new-hostage-release-proposal/0000018c-f87b-d517-af9d-fc7f5e340000</guid></item><item><title>1986年以来失踪士兵的女儿罗恩·阿拉德：以色列政界人士必须就释放人质进行谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/daughter-of-soldier-missing-since-1986-israel-must-negotiate-for-hostages-release/0000018c-f7d0-d432-a7ae-fff972390000</link><description>尤瓦尔·阿拉德在脸书上写道，“因为历史不仅在我眼前重演，而且人们似乎拒绝从历史中吸取教训”，并警告应立即将人质带回家</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 12:10:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/daughter-of-soldier-missing-since-1986-israel-must-negotiate-for-hostages-release/0000018c-f7d0-d432-a7ae-fff972390000</guid></item></channel></rss>